U.K. Banking Commission May Urge Competition Probe, Sky Reports

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-04-07T02:06:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/u-k-banking-commission-may-urge-competition-probe-sky-reports.html
The U.K. Independent Commission on
Banking may say in its interim report next week that a full-
scale competition investigation is an option it will consider
recommending in the next phase of its work, Sky News City Editor
Mark Kleinman reported in his online blog.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
